An official website of the United States Government Department of Health & Human Services

Official websites use .gov

Federal government websites often end in .gov or .mil. Before sharing sensitive information, make sure you're on a federal government site.

Secure .gov websites use HTTPS

A lock ( Lock Locked padlock icon ) or https:// ensures that you are connecting to the official website and that any information you provide is encrypted and transmitted securely.
